"For Task 3, I explored coding and collaboration platforms essential for an AI & ML student. First, I used HackerRank to complete a Python challenge.
Solving the addition challenge helped me understand the platform's layout, which I plan to use regularly for practicing Python and preparing for future internships.

Secondly, I created a 'Digital Literacy Awareness Quiz' using Google Forms. I designed five questions to test my peers' knowledge of online safety and professional tools. 
I also linked the form to a Google Sheet to see how responses are automatically recorded. 
These tools are very helpful for my academic life because they allow me to collect data and collaborate with my group members on university projects easily. 
Mastering these platforms makes me feel more confident as a Student Digital Ambassador."
